The '''Traders' Coalition''' was an organization in the [[Atzerri system/Legends|Atzerri system]] specializing in trade. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], the Coalition hired the infamous [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] to capture the dealer [[H'buk]], who stole 400,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].

